welcome_message_body: Welcome to Roseville, a charming city known for its beautiful parks, vibrant downtown area, and friendly community. We hope you have a wonderful time exploring all that Roseville has to offer!

terminals.name: Main Terminal

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Yuba County Airport serves all commercial flights and includes a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Yuba County Airport caters to private and charter flights, providing a more exclusive and personalized experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.description: The main terminal at Beale AFB Airport serves both commercial and military flights.
